// Schema-guided serde-eure roundtrip for records that allow unknown fields.

input_eure = ```eure
name = "Grace"
extra = "kept"
metadata = { active => true, tags => ["alpha", "beta"] }
```

schema = ```eure
name = `text`
$unknown-fields = "allow"
```

json = ```json
